;s:5:\"1.1.6\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.1.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.7\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.1.7.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.8\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.1.8.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.9\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.1.9.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.0\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.2.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.1\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.2.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.2\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.2.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.3\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.2.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.4\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.2.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.5\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.2.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.6\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.2.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.0\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.3.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.1\";s:81:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.1.3.1.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:75:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:85:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote/assets/icon-128x128.jpg?rev=1460947\";}s:12:\"contributors\";a:0:{}}}s:33:\"yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews\";a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"YITH Woocommerce Advanced Reviews\";s:4:\"slug\";s:33:\"yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews\";s:15:\"premium_constat\";s:17:\"YITH_YWAR_PREMIUM\";s:4:\"file\";s:8:\"init.php\";s:7:\"wp_info\";a:26:{s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews\";s:4:\"slug\";s:33:\"yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.2.8\";s:6:\"author\";s:43:\"<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/\">YITHEMES</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.7.5\";s:6:\"rating\";d:82;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:11;i:4;i:2;i:3;i:1;i:2;i:3;i:1;i:1;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:18;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:2;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:6000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:143258;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:22:\"2017-05-30 10:43am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-01-23\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:69:\"http://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:2726:\"<p>Add a histogram table to the reviews of your products, such as you see in most trendy e-commerce sites, and give users the possibility to attach images to their reviews. Keep up-to-date about most trendy products thanks to the new options conceived to manage an advanced review system.</p>\n<h4>Detail, feedback and customisability in one plugin only</h4>\n<p>YITH Woocommerce Advanced Reviews offers something more than the traditional displaying of product review and rating.<br />\nIt allows your users to add a title and one or more attachments to their reviews. Furthermore, a summary is generated for each product with an indication of how many reviews have been written for each different rating.</p>\n<p>Research states that other users&#8217; reviews are the primary information, together with product price obviously, that drives them to buy an item or not. Let your users discover what other users say about the product.</p>\n<h4>Main features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Convert standard reviews in YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews new format.</li>\n<li>Add rich snippets to the reviews.</li>\n<li>Let your customers add a title when writing a product review.</li>\n<li>Let you customers attach some image as attachment to the product review.</li>\n<li>Choose how many files can be appended for a single product review.</li>\n<li>Add review summary bar with statistics about how many times a rating of 1,2,3,4 or 5 stars was submitted.</li>\n<li>Customize look and feel.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For a more detailed list of options and features of the plugin, please look at the <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/\" title=\"Yith WooCommerce Advanced Reviews official documentation\" rel=\"nofollow\">official documentation</a>.</p>\n<p>Discover all the features of the plugin and install it in your theme: the result will be extremely satisfying.</p>\n<h3>Suggestions</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress\" title=\"Translating WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/contact/\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews languages.</p>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:716:\"<p>Important: before of all you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for Yith WooCommerce Advanced Reviews to be working. If WooCommerce plugin is active, you just need to activate the Yith WooCommerce Advanced Reviews plugin.</p>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews will add a new tab called &#8220;Advanced Reviews&#8221; inside the YIT Plugins menu item. There you are able to configure all plugin settings.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:1874:\"<ul>\n<li>What happens to the already available reviews if I activate your plugin?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All the already available reviews of the system are easily convertible in the YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews format with the specific feature.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Can I upgrade free version plugin to premium?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Of course. It&#8217;s easy. Go to this page, purchase premium version and install it into your theme. Activating the premium version, you will automatically deactivate the free one.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Do I lose the settings of the free version if I activate the premium one?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>No, the premium version will keep in memory your settings, while new features will be unlocked.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Can i overwrite templates plugin?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Of course, you can overwrite templates and add features through the specific hook.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Can I customize the plugin for a better theme integration?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can customize some visual attribute from the plugin option. For better integration, you can both overwrite the template and customize the look and feel writing your own CSS rules.</p>\n\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Important: before of all you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for Yith WooCommerce Advanced Reviews to be working. If WooCommerce plugin is active, you just need to activate the Yith WooCommerce Advanced Reviews plugin.</p>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews will add a new tab called &#8220;Advanced Reviews&#8221; inside the YIT Plugins menu item. There you are able to configure all plugin settings.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:4361:\"<h4>Version 1.2.8 &#8211; Released: May 30, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: average rating shown twice on review&#8217;s summary.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.7 &#8211; Released: Apr 30, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: YITH Plugin Framework.</li>\n<li>Tweak: tested up to WordPress 4.7.4.</li>\n<li>Tweak: changed plugin tags.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.6 &#8211; Released: Apr 05, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: added missing $customer_reviews_label var in ywar-single-product-reviews.php template.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.5 &#8211; Released: Mar 16, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New:  Support to WooCommerce 2.7.0-RC1</li>\n<li>Update: YITH Plugin Framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.4 &#8211; Released: Jan 16, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: WordPress 4.7 ready</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.3 &#8211; Released: Jun 13, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: italian localization</li>\n<li>New: spanish localization</li>\n<li>Fixed: unable to edit the review from the review title link</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.2 &#8211; Released: May 04, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: missing YITH Plugin FW files</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1 &#8211; Released: May 02, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: plugin compatible with WordPress 4.5</li>\n<li>Updated: YITH plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.0 &#8211; Released: Feb 26, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: conflict with YITH WooCommerce Gift Cards that prevents the sending of attachments</li>\n<li>Fixed: prevent a function from being declared twice</li>\n<li>New: filter yith_advanced_reviews_review_content_elements to let third party plugin or theme change the elements to be shown</li>\n<li>Updated: YITH plugin FW</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.9 &#8211; Released: Nov 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: changed action used for YITH plugin framework loading</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.8 &#8211; Released: Oct 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: YITH plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.7 &#8211; Released: Oct 07, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: changed text-domain to yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.6 &#8211; Released: Sep 23, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: improved query performance for low resources server.</li>\n<li>Fix: sometimes items was not shown clicking on a view on reviews back end page.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.5 &#8211; Released: Sep 04, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: CSS issue on pages other than &#8220;Reviews&#8221; page.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.4 &#8211; Released: Aug 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: update YITH Plugin framework.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.3 &#8211; Released: May 12 , 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: when the review author is unknown, it was shown admin user as content author.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.2 &#8211; Released: May 11 , 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Custom template are fully overwritable from theme files.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.1 &#8211; Released: May 07 , 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Call to undefined function session_status for previous PHP version.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.0 &#8211; Released: May 06 , 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: advanced reviews custom post type.</li>\n<li>New: check the review status from a single page.</li>\n<li>New: filter the reviews by status or update the status with bulk actions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.8 &#8211; Released: Apr 14, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: updated documentation</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.7 &#8211; Released: Feb 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Woocommerce 2.3 support</li>\n<li>Tweak: String translation</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.6 &#8211; Released: Feb 06, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Buttons with WooCommerce style</li>\n<li>Fixed: &#8220;Load more&#8221; button style strong appearance</li>\n<li>Tweak: Review summary overwritten by theme</li>\n<li>Tweak: Theme compatibility improvement</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>VERSION 1.0.5 &#8211; Released: Feb 04, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>VERSION 1.0.4 &#8211; Released: Feb 02, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>VERSION 1.0.3 &#8211; Released: Jan 30, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Plugin core framework</li>\n<li>Tweak: Theme integration</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>VERSION 1.0.2 &#8211; Released: Dec 29, 2014</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Yit_Plugin_Panel_WooCommerce class do not exists.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>VERSION 1.0.1 &#8211; Released: Dec 23, 20141.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: Plugin core framework</li>\n<li>Tweak: Plugin options page</li>\n<li>Fixed: Minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:3873:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"This is the general setting page, you can find it in &quot;YIT Plugins&quot; menu item. There you can set if a title should be shown on review submit form and on review content. You can also set if enable attachments and how many files the client is allowed to append.\"></a><p>This is the general setting page, you can find it in \"YIT Plugins\" menu item. There you can set if a title should be shown on review submit form and on review content. You can also set if enable attachments and how many files the client is allowed to append.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"Convert all previously created reviews to YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews format, without losing any data.\"></a><p>Convert all previously created reviews to YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews format, without losing any data.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"Customize the summary bar background, foreground and text color and if the percentage value must be shown inside the percentage bars.\"></a><p>Customize the summary bar background, foreground and text color and if the percentage value must be shown inside the percentage bars.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"Manage all reviews from a dedicated page.\"></a><p>Manage all reviews from a dedicated page.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"Order reviews by rating from highest to lowest, and vice versa.\"></a><p>Order reviews by rating from highest to lowest, and vice versa.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"Edit reviews with bulk actions.\"></a><p>Edit reviews with bulk actions.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"Submit form is extended to allow users to add a title and one or more attachments files.\"></a><p>Submit form is extended to allow users to add a title and one or more attachments files.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"This is how an advanced review with additional title and attached thumbnail looks like.\"></a><p>This is how an advanced review with additional title and attached thumbnail looks like.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-9.png?rev=1606388\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-9.png?rev=1606388\" alt=\"Review summary is shown before review list. It displays statistics about the rating chosen by users submitting reviews.\"></a><p>Review summary is shown before review list. It displays statistics about the rating chosen by users submitting reviews.</p></li></ol>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:139:\"Extends the WooCommerce reviews and add a histogram table to the reviews of your products, such as you see in most trendy e-commerce sites.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.8.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:9:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1606388\";s:7:\"caption\";s:258:\"This is the general setting page, you can find it in \"YIT Plugins\" menu item. There you can set if a title should be shown on review submit form and on review content. You can also set if enable attachments and how many files the client is allowed to append.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1606388\";s:7:\"caption\";s:108:\"Convert all previously created reviews to YITH WooCommerce Advanced Reviews format, without losing any data.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1606388\";s:7:\"caption\";s:133:\"Customize the summary bar background, foreground and text color and if the percentage value must be shown inside the percentage bars.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1606388\";s:7:\"caption\";s:41:\"Manage all reviews from a dedicated page.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1606388\";s:7:\"caption\";s:63:\"Order reviews by rating from highest to lowest, and vice versa.\";}i:6;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=1606388\";s:7:\"caption\";s:31:\"Edit reviews with bulk actions.\";}i:7;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-7.png?rev=1606388\";s:7:\"caption\";s:88:\"Submit form is extended to allow users to add a title and one or more attachments files.\";}i:8;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-8.png?rev=1606388\";s:7:\"caption\";s:87:\"This is how an advanced review with additional title and attached thumbnail looks like.\";}i:9;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/screenshot-9.png?rev=1606388\";s:7:\"caption\";s:119:\"Review summary is shown before review list. It displays statistics about the rating chosen by users submitting reviews.\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:4:{s:7:\"comment\";s:7:\"comment\";s:6:\"rating\";s:6:\"rating\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:26:{s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.5\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.0.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.6\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.0.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.7\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.0.7.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.8\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.0.8.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.3\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.4\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.5\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.6\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.7\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.7.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.8\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.8.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.9\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.1.9.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.0\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.1\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.2\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.3\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.4\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.5\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.6\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.7\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.7.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.8\";s:82:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.1.2.8.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:76:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:86:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-advanced-reviews/assets/icon-128x128.jpg?rev=1461228\";}s:12:\"contributors\";a:0:{}}}s:24:\"yith-woocommerce-compare\";a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:24:\"YITH WooCommerce Compare\";s:4:\"slug\";s:24:\"yith-woocommerce-compare\";s:15:\"premium_constat\";s:23:\"YITH_WOOCOMPARE_PREMIUM\";s:4:\"file\";s:8:\"init.php\";s:7:\"wp_info\";a:26:{s:4:\"name\";s:24:\"YITH WooCommerce Compare\";s:4:\"slug\";s:24:\"yith-woocommerce-compare\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"2.2.1\";s:6:\"author\";s:44:\"<a href=\"https://yithemes.com/\">YITHEMES</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:5:\"3.5.1\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.8.1\";s:6:\"rating\";d:88;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:19;i:4;i:3;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:3;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:25;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:5;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:1;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:100000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:1256899;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:21:\"2017-07-05 1:55pm GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2013-06-24\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:61:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:4:{s:11:\"description\";s:2640:\"<p>YITH WooCommerce Compare plugin is an extension of WooCommerce plugin that allow your users to compare some products of your shop.<br />\nAll products are saved in one complete table where the user can see the difference between the products. Each product features can be<br />\nset with the woocommerce attributes in the product configuration.<br />\nYou can also add a simple widget with the list of products the users have added, where you can manage them.<br />\nAlso you can simply customize the compare table with your style, by editing the specific template.</p>\n<p>Full documentation is available <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>This plugin is 100% compatible with <a href=\"http://wpml.org/?aid=24889&amp;affiliate_key=Qn1wDeBNTcZV\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPML</a></p>\n<h4>Installation</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Compare</code> from Plugins page</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Add the features in each product by setting the attributes in prouct configuration;</li>\n<li>Configure the options in YIT Plugin -&gt; Compare;</li>\n<li>The user of your shop will click in the &#8220;Compare&#8221; button located in the single product page;</li>\n<li>Will be open a popup with the compare table inside.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>You can also add the widget with the product list of compare table, in Appearance -&gt; Widgets and adding the widget &#8220;YITH WooCommerce Compare Widget&#8221;.</p>\n<h3>Suggestions</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Compare, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Compare.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English (Default)</li>\n<li>Italiano</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress\" title=\"Translating WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/contact/\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH WooCommerce Compare Languages.</p>\n<h3>Tài liệu</h3>\n<p>Full documentation is available <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:1547:\"\n<h4>Can I customize the compare table?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, you can copy the template from the plugin folder and paste it inside the folder &#8220;woocommerce&#8221; of your theme folder.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Can I select what fields show inside the compare table?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, you can choose what fields to show in the compare table. You can do it in YIT Plugins -&gt; Compare.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Can I order the fields in the compare table?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, you can sort the fields in the compare table. You can do it in YIT Plugins -&gt; Compare.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>What are the main changes in plugin translation?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Recently YITH WooCommerce Compare has been selected to be included in the &#8220;translate.wordpress.org&#8221; translate programme.<br />\nIn order to import correctly the plugin strings in the new system, we had to change the text domain form &#8216;yit&#8217; to &#8216;yith-woocommerce-compare&#8217;.<br />\nOnce the plugin will be imported in the translate.wordpress.org system, the translations of other languages will be downloaded directly from WordPress, without using any .po and .mo files. Moreover, users will be able to participate in a more direct way to plugin translations, suggesting texts in their languages in the dedicated tab on translate.wordpress.org.<br />\nDuring this transition step, .po and .mo files will be used as always, but in order to be recognized by WordPress, they will need to have a new nomenclature, renaming them in:<br />\nyith-woocommerce-compare-.po<br />\nyith-woocommerce-compare-.mo</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:5976:\"<h4>2.2.1</h4>\n<p>Released on Jul 05, 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.1.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.8.</li>\n<li>New: Russian Translation.</li>\n<li>New: Slovenian Translation.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Update: Language Files.</li>\n<li>Fix: WPML and Add to cart action from popup.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.2.0</h4>\n<p>Released on Mar 29, 2017</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.0.0 RC2.</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.7.3</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Update: Language Files.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.1.0</h4>\n<p>Released on Oct 19, 2016</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.6.4</li>\n<li>New: Support to WordPress 4.6</li>\n<li>New: Auto remove from compare list for products that are private or were cancelled.</li>\n<li>New: Add as default fields Weight and Dimensions.</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Update: Language Files.</li>\n<li>Fix: Uncaught ReferenceError &#8220;redirect_to_cart is not defined&#8221; error on &#8220;add to cart&#8221; action.</li>\n<li>Fix: Compatibility issue with NextGen Gallery plugin.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.9</h4>\n<p>Released on Jun 13, 2016</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.6 RC1</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.8</h4>\n<p>Released on Apr 19, 2016</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Compatibility with WordPress 4.5</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Fix: Fatal error call to undefined method WC_AJAX::get_endpoint() for WooCommerce version older then 2.4</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.7</h4>\n<p>Released on Apr 01, 2016</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: Plugin template compare.php</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core.</li>\n<li>Update: Language file.</li>\n<li>Fix: Product status now updates automatically when the product is removed from the compare widget.</li>\n<li>Fix: Redirect correctly to cart page after &#8220;Add to cart&#8221; is clicked if &#8220;Redirect to the cart page after successful addition&#8221; option is enabled.</li>\n<li>Fix: Redirect correctly to product page after &#8220;Add to cart&#8221; is clicked when &#8220;Enable AJAX add to cart buttons on archives&#8221; option is disabled.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.6</h4>\n<p>Released on Jan 11, 2016</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Compatibility with WooCommerce 2.5 RC</li>\n<li>Update: Change ajax call fron admin-ajax to wc-ajax</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin template compare.php</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.5</h4>\n<p>Released on Oct 30, 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core</li>\n<li>Fix: After you remove product from compare, you can re-add it without reload page</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.4</h4>\n<p>Released on Sep 22, 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: Changed Text Domain from &#8216;yith-wcmp&#8217; to &#8216;yith-woocommerce-compare&#8217;</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core Framework</li>\n<li>Fix: JS error when loading compare window</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.3</h4>\n<p>Released on Aug 21, 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Compatibility with WooPress 4.3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.2</h4>\n<p>Released on Aug 12, 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Compatibility with WooCommerce 2.4</li>\n<li>Update: Core plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.1</h4>\n<p>Released on Aug 10, 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: Core plugin</li>\n<li>Fix: Compare table layout</li>\n<li>Fix: undefined function unblock() in main js</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>2.0.0</h4>\n<p>Released on Jul 15, 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: New plugin core</li>\n<li>Update: Language files</li>\n<li>Removed: old default.po catalog language file</li>\n<li>Fix: Error in class yith-woocompare-fontend</li>\n<li>Fix: Lightbox doesn&#8217;t close after click view cart</li>\n<li>Fix: minor bug fix</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.3</h4>\n<p>Released on Feb 13, 2015</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Bulgarian Translation by Joanna Mikova</li>\n<li>New: Spanish Translation by Rodoslav Angelov and Mariano Rivas</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2</h4>\n<p>Released on Dec 03, 2014</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Shortcode compare</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.1</h4>\n<p>Released on Sep 17, 2014</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WC 2.2.3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.0</h4>\n<p>Released on Sep 16, 2014</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WC 2.2.2</li>\n<li>Update: Compare Template</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin Core Framework</li>\n<li>Fix: Fields orders</li>\n<li>Tweek: WPML Support improved</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.4</h4>\n<p>Released on Jun 30, 2014</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: Colorbox Library Version 1.5.10</li>\n<li>Fix: Horizontal scroll bar issue: show at the end of iframe</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.3</h4>\n<p>Released on Jun 05, 2014</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: RTL Support</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2</h4>\n<p>Released on Mar 21, 2014</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: WPML Support on Compare Widget</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1</h4>\n<p>Released on Feb 19, 2014</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Add to cart Button on Compare page</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0</h4>\n<p>Released on Feb 13, 2014</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.1.X</li>\n<li>New: French translation by Paumo</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.5</h4>\n<p>Released on Oct 14, 2013</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Persian translation by Khalil Delavaran</li>\n<li>New: Compare table title option</li>\n<li>New: Compatibility with WPML plugin</li>\n<li>New: Brazilian Portuguese translation by hotelwww</li>\n<li>Fix: Responsive features</li>\n<li>Fix: Dequeued wrong JS scripts</li>\n<li>Update: Dutch translation by Frans Pronk</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<p>Released on Sep 04, 2013</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: complete Dutch translation. Thanks to Frans Pronk</li>\n<li>Fix: Sortable scripts included only in the plugin admin page</li>\n<li>Fix: products list in popup don&#8217;t update after have added a product</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<p>Released on Jul 31, 2013</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor bugs fixes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<p>Released on Jul 20, 2013</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: trigger in javascript file for add to compare event</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<p>Released on Jun 27, 2013</p>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Link/Button text option in plugin options</li>\n<li>New: ability to add a link in the menu top open the popup</li>\n<li>Fix: bug with attributes added after installation</li>\n<li>Fix: bug with plugin activated but not working for multisites</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<p>Released on Jun 24, 2013</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:761:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1625811\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1625811\" alt=\"The popup with compare table.\"></a><p>The popup with compare table.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1625811\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1625811\" alt=\"The button compare.\"></a><p>The button compare.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1625811\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1625811\" alt=\"The settings of plugin\"></a><p>The settings of plugin</p></li></ol>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:129:\"YITH WooCommerce Compare allows you to compare more products of your shop in one complete table.\nWooCommerce Compatible up to 3.1\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.2.1.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1625811\";s:7:\"caption\";s:29:\"The popup with compare table.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1625811\";s:7:\"caption\";s:19:\"The button compare.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1625811\";s:7:\"caption\";s:22:\"The settings of plugin\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:16:\"compare-products\";s:16:\"compare products\";s:13:\"compare-table\";s:13:\"compare table\";s:15:\"product-compare\";s:15:\"product compare\";s:18:\"product-comparison\";s:18:\"product comparison\";s:19:\"woocommerce-compare\";s:19:\"woocommerce compare\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:29:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.5\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.0.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.3\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.4\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.1.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.0\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.2.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.1\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.2.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.2\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.2.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.3\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.1.2.3.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.0\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.1\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.2\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.3\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.4\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.5\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.5.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.6\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.6.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.7\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.7.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.8\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.8.zip\";s:5:\"2.0.9\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.0.9.zip\";s:5:\"2.1.0\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"2.2.0\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.2.0.zip\";s:5:\"2.2.1\";s:73:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.2.2.1.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:67:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-compare.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:77:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-compare/assets/icon-128x128.jpg?rev=1460909\";}s:12:\"contributors\";a:0:{}}}s:29:\"yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode\";a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:29:\"YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode\";s:4:\"slug\";s:29:\"yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode\";s:15:\"premium_constat\";s:13:\"YWCTM_PREMIUM\";s:4:\"file\";s:8:\"init.php\";s:7:\"wp_info\";a:26:{s:4:\"name\";s:29:\"YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode\";s:4:\"slug\";s:29:\"yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.5.5\";s:6:\"author\";s:43:\"<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/\">YITHEMES</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.7.5\";s:6:\"rating\";i:80;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:12;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:4;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:16;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:1;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:20000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:175725;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:22:\"2017-03-23 11:34am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-02-19\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:65:\"http://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:5217:\"<p>YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode is one of our most appealing plugins for WordPress and WooCommerce users who need to switch their WooCommerce site into an online catalogue for some time. Reasons for this switch may be a thousand, but most common ones are concerned with the need of users to perform maintenance actions in their warehouse without putting their site offline. Is it ever happened to you to take inventory and have to put your WooCommerce shop down? How many potential customers lost! A catalogue gives you the opportunity to leave your WooCommerce products online and to let your customers contact you anyway for whatever question they might have. This increases customers&#8217; loyalty and you do not lose visibility online.</p>\n<h4>Features of YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Enable/disable YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode from option panel</li>\n<li>Choose if admin sees the store as catalog (when set) Mode settings for administrators also</li>\n<li>Hide &#8220;Add to Cart&#8221; button in WooCommerce product detail page</li>\n<li>Hide &#8220;Add to Cart&#8221; button in the other pages of the site (catalog, shop etc.)</li>\n<li>Hide WooCommerce &#8220;Cart&#8221; and &#8220;Checkout&#8221; pages and any reference to them</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Official documentation of YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode</h4>\n<p>For a more detailed description of options and features of YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode, please, read the <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/\" rel=\"nofollow\">official documentation</a>.</p>\n<h4>Compatibility with WooCommerce plugins</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode has been tested and compatibility is certain with the following WooCommerce plugins that you can add to your site:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-request-a-quote/\">YITH WooCommerce Request A Quote</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-quick-view/\">YITH WooCommerce Quick View</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/\">YITH WooCommerce Badge Management</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-tab-manager/\">YITH WooCommerce Tab Manager</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>An essential kit for your WooCommerce site?</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode is available in combination with many other plugins in <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-essential-kit-for-woocommerce-1/\"><strong>YITH Essential Kit for WooCommerce #1</strong></a>, a bundle of indispensable tools to make your WooCommerce site look more professional and be more user-friendly. Learn more about all WooCommerce plugins included and boost your WooCommerce site with a simple click!</p>\n<h4>Premium features of YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>All features of the free version</li>\n<li>Enable/disable catalog mode without having to disable YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode.</li>\n<li>Do not apply catalog mode to selected WooCommerce products added in the “Exclusion list”. Exclusions are managed from “Exclusions” tab</li>\n<li>Set options for WooCommerce products in “Exclusion list”, to which catalog mode is not applied</li>\n<li>Reverse functioning of “Exclusion list”, by applying catalog mode only to WooCommerce products added in the list</li>\n<li>Hide WooCommerce “Cart” and “Checkout” pages and any other possible reference to them</li>\n<li>Hide WooCommerce product price</li>\n<li>Enter an alternative text to replace WooCommerce product price (e.g. “Register to see price”)</li>\n<li>Hide WooCommerce price to all users or to unregistered users only</li>\n<li>Add a tab with an inquiry form for each WooCommerce product to let your users contact you and ask about it</li>\n<li>Include the link of the WooCommerce product page from which the inquiry email has been sent</li>\n<li>Custom button in WooCommerce product page</li>\n<li>Select an action for the button added by YITH Woocommerce Catalog Mode (generic URL, email address, phone number, Skype contact)</li>\n<li>Disable WooCommerce “Reviews” tab in product page for all users or for unregistered users only</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Suggestions</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<p><strong>NOTE: The translation process of this plugin has been changed by WordPress. Please, read the correlated FAQ to be updated about the news changes.</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n<li>Dutch (by Bart Verkerk)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress\" title=\"Translating WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/contact/\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode languages.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:718:\"<h4>Installation</h4>\n<p>Important: before of all you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode to be working. If WooCommerce plugin is active, you just need to activate the YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode plugin.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode will add a new tab called &#8220;Catalog Mode&#8221; inside the YIT Plugins menu item. There you are able to configure all plugin settings.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:3317:\"\n<h4>Is it compatible with all WordPress themes?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Compatibility with all themes is impossible, because they are too many, but generally if themes are developed according to WordPress and WooCommerce guidelines, YITH plugins are compatible with them.<br />\nYet, we can grant compatibility with themes developed by YIThemes, because they are constantly updated and tested with our plugins. Sometimes, especially when new versions are released, it might only require some time for them to be all updated, but you can be sure that they will be tested and will be working in a few days.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>How can I get support if my WooCommerce plugin is not working?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>If you have problems with our plugins or something is not working as it should, first follow this preliminary steps:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Test the plugin with a WordPress default theme, to be sure that the error is not caused by the theme you are currently using.</li>\n<li>Deactivate all plugins you are using and check if the problem is still occurring.</li>\n<li>Ensure that you plugin version, your theme version and your WordPress and WooCommerce version (if required) are updated and that the problem you are experiencing has not already been solved in a later plugin update.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If none of the previous listed actions helps you solve the problem, then, submit a ticket in the forum and describe your problem accurately, specify WordPress and WooCommerce versions you are using and any other information that might help us solve your problem as quickly as possible. Thanks!</p>\n</p>\n<h4>How can I get more features for my WooCommerce plugin?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can get more features with the premium version of YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode, available on <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode\" rel=\"nofollow\">YIThemes page</a>. Here you can read more about the premium features of the plugin and make it give it its best shot!</p>\n</p>\n<h4>How can I try the full-featured plugin?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>If you want to see a demonstration version of the premium plugin, you can see that in <a href=\"http://plugins.yithemes.com/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode\" rel=\"nofollow\">this page</a>. Browse it and try all options available so that you can see how your plugin looks like.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>What are the main changes in plugin translation?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Recently YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode has been selected to be included in the &#8220;translate.wordpress.org&#8221; translate programme.<br />\nIn order to import correctly the plugin strings in the new system, we had to change the text domain form &#8216;ywctm&#8217; to &#8216;yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode&#8217;.<br />\nOnce the plugin will be imported in the translate.wordpress.org system, the translations of other languages will be downloaded directly from WordPress, without using any .po and .mo files. Moreover, users will be able to participate in a more direct way to plugin translations, suggesting texts in their languages in the dedicated tab on translate.wordpress.org.<br />\nDuring this transition step, .po and .mo files will be used as always, but in order to be recognized by WordPress, they will need to have a new nomenclature, renaming them in:<br />\nyith-woocommerce-catalog-mode-.po<br />\nyith-woocommerce-catalog-mode-.mo</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:3601:\"<h4>Version 1.5.5 &#8211; Released: Mar 23, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Support for WooCommerce 3.0.0-RC 1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.4.0 &#8211; Released: May 31, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Tested with WooCommerce 2.6.0 beta 3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.7 &#8211; Released: May 13, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: filter &#8220;ywctm_cart_widget_classes&#8221; to hide the cart widget</li>\n<li>Remove: yith-catalog-mode.css and yith-catalog-mode.min.css files</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.5 &#8211; Released: Apr 13, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: compatibility with WordPress 4.5</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.3 &#8211; Released: Apr 08, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: minified versions of CSS files</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.2 &#8211; Released: Mar 09, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.1 &#8211; Released: Mar 04, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: items excluded not added to cart</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.0 &#8211; Released: Mar 01, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: language file</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.4 &#8211; Released: Feb 19, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.3 &#8211; Released: Jan 22, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: compatibility with WooCommerce 2.5</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.2 &#8211; Released: Dec 16, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: compatibility with YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1 &#8211; Released: Dec 15, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.0 &#8211; Released: Oct 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Dutch translation (by Bart Verkerk)</li>\n<li>Fix: options panel more user friendly</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.5 &#8211; Released: Oct 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.4 &#8211; Released: Oct 07, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: changed text domain from ywctm to yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode</li>\n<li>Update: changed all language file for the new text domain</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.3 &#8211; Released: Sept 25, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Various code improvements</li>\n<li>Update: language file</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.2 &#8211; Released: Aug 25, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: compatibility with YITH Essential Kit for WooCommerce #1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.1 &#8211; Released: Aug 13, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.0 &#8211; Released: Aug 13, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.4</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.9 &#8211; Released: July 20, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: YITH WooCommerce Colors and Labels Variations compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.8 &#8211; Released: July 09, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update language file</li>\n<li>Fix: YITH WooCommerce Quick View compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.7 &#8211; Released: Jun 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Added functions for themes and plugins compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.6 &#8211; Released: May 22, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Added functions for themes compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.5 &#8211; Released: May 06, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Product variations bug</li>\n<li>Fix: Custom button bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.4 &#8211; Released: May 05, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.3 &#8211; Released: Apr 10, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Improved code performance</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.2 &#8211; Released: Mar 11, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Added functions for themes compatibility</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 &#8211; Released: Mar 02, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: Minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 &#8211; Released: Feb 19, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:1765:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625665\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625665\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;This is the settings page of YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode, you can find it in YIT Plugins menu item. You can hide WooCommerce &quot;Add to Cart&quot; buttons and WooCommerce Cart and Checkout pages.&lt;/p&gt;\"></a><p><p>This is the settings page of YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode, you can find it in YIT Plugins menu item. You can hide WooCommerce \"Add to Cart\" buttons and WooCommerce Cart and Checkout pages.</p></p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625665\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625665\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;This image shows the shop page as it appears when WooCommerce &quot;Add to Cart&quot; button is hidden and WooCommerce Cart and Checkout page are deactivated.&lt;/p&gt;\"></a><p><p>This image shows the shop page as it appears when WooCommerce \"Add to Cart\" button is hidden and WooCommerce Cart and Checkout page are deactivated.</p></p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1625665\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1625665\" alt=\"&lt;p&gt;This image shows WooCommerce product detail page as it appears when WooCommerce &quot;Add to Cart&quot; button is hidden and WooCommerce Cart and Checkout page are deactivated.&lt;/p&gt;\"></a><p><p>This image shows WooCommerce product detail page as it appears when WooCommerce \"Add to Cart\" button is hidden and WooCommerce Cart and Checkout page are deactivated.</p></p></li></ol>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:135:\"YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode, a plugin for disabling sales in your e-commerce and turn it into an e-commerce into an online catalogue.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.5.5.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:82:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=1625665\";s:7:\"caption\";s:196:\"<p>This is the settings page of YITH WooCommerce Catalog Mode, you can find it in YIT Plugins menu item. You can hide WooCommerce \"Add to Cart\" buttons and WooCommerce Cart and Checkout pages.</p>\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:82:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=1625665\";s:7:\"caption\";s:155:\"<p>This image shows the shop page as it appears when WooCommerce \"Add to Cart\" button is hidden and WooCommerce Cart and Checkout page are deactivated.</p>\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:82:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/screenshot-3.jpg?rev=1625665\";s:7:\"caption\";s:173:\"<p>This image shows WooCommerce product detail page as it appears when WooCommerce \"Add to Cart\" button is hidden and WooCommerce Cart and Checkout page are deactivated.</p>\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:8:\"products\";s:8:\"products\";s:6:\"themes\";s:6:\"themes\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:31:\"woocommerce-catalog-mode-plugin\";s:31:\"woocommerce catalog mode plugin\";s:24:\"woocommerce-catalog-only\";s:24:\"woocommerce catalog only\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:30:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.5\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.6\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.7\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.7.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.8\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.8.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.9\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.0.9.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.3\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.4\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.1.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.5\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.1.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.0\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.2.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.1\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.2.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.2\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.2.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.3\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.2.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.4\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.2.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.0\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.3.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.1\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.3.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.2\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.3.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.3\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.3.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.5\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.3.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.7\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.3.7.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.0\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.4.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.5.5\";s:78:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.1.5.5.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:72:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:82:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-catalog-mode/assets/icon-128x128.jpg?rev=1466776\";}s:12:\"contributors\";a:0:{}}}s:31:\"yith-woocommerce-order-tracking\";a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:31:\"YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking\";s:4:\"slug\";s:31:\"yith-woocommerce-order-tracking\";s:15:\"premium_constat\";s:17:\"YITH_YWOT_PREMIUM\";s:4:\"file\";s:8:\"init.php\";s:7:\"wp_info\";a:26:{s:4:\"name\";s:31:\"YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking\";s:4:\"slug\";s:31:\"yith-woocommerce-order-tracking\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:6:\"author\";s:43:\"<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/\">YITHEMES</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.7.5\";s:6:\"rating\";d:76;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:3;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:1;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:1;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:5;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:4;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:8000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:114125;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:22:\"2017-04-30 10:01am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-02-02\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:67:\"http://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:6013:\"<p>YITH Woocommerce Order Tracking is a WordPress plugin that allows you to manage easily shipping information concerning your orders and that lets your customers be notified about their order shipping.<br />\nJust put yourself in your customers&#8217; shoes: you make an order on a WooCommerce watch store and you can&#8217;t wait for your watch to be delivered to you. WooCommerce plugin allows you to place orders, to let you pay, but after that?<br />\nThe seller can give you information about how long will your product take to be delivered, but you are not sure about where it is until it arrives. What you need is something informing you about the packet, a tracking tool, that WooCommerce unfortunately does not adds automatically to a shop. This is exactly what YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking allows you to do, tracking the delivery of your watches, clothes, books or whatever WooCommerce product you have ordered.<br />\nThis is a very useful tool to make your WooCommerce shop as complete as possible and offer your customers the best service, they feel you care of them and they feel safe: this will certainly make sales in your WooCommerce shop increase dramatically.</p>\n<h4>Save precious time and feel free to focus only on your business activity</h4>\n<p>Moreover, it is a great advantage for you too, because with a plugin such as YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking you do not have to spend your precious time to manage telephone calls and emails from your customers, who want to know if their WooCommerce order has been shipped.<br />\nDevote yourself and your time to more profitable activities for your WooCommerce shop and make communication with your customers be managed automatically each time one of your orders is set as &#8220;shipped&#8221;.</p>\n<h4>Main features of YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Do you ship your WooCommerce orders always or mainly with the same carrier? You don&#8217;t have to add this information each time: every shipping will be arranged with the default carrier.</li>\n<li>Customize the message you want to show to your users in details of your WooCommerce orders.</li>\n<li>Use some placeholders to fill automatically carrier&#8217;s details, the tracking code and the shipping date for your WooCommerce orders.</li>\n<li>Choose the place in order detail page where showing the tracking message to your WooCommerce users: you can place it before or after order content.</li>\n<li>Manage easily tracking details of the shipping from the related page in WooCommerce back end.</li>\n<li>Identify smoothly which WooCommerce orders have been shipped and which are pending from &#8220;Orders&#8221; page created in WooCommerce back end.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For a more detailed list of options and features of the plugin, please read the <a href=\"http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/\" title=\"Yith WooCommerce Order Tracking official documentation\" rel=\"nofollow\">official documentation</a>.</p>\n<p>Discover all the features of YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking and install it in your theme: the result will be extremely satisfying.</p>\n<h4>Compatibility with WooCommerce plugins</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking has been tested and compatibility is certain with the following WooCommerce plugins that you can add to your site:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-pdf-invoice/\" title=\"Generate and send PDF invoices and shipping list documents for WooCommerce orders via email.\">YITH WooCommerce PDF Invoice and Shipping List</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-bulk-product-editing/\" title=\"YITH WooCommerce Bulk Product Editing allows you to edit the prices of different prod\">YITH WooCommerce Bulk Product Editing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-product-bundles/\" title=\"YITH WooCommerce Product Bundles allows you to bundle WooCommerce products and sell them with a unique price.\">YITH WooCommerce Product Bundles</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>An essential kit for your WooCommerce site?</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking is available in combination with many other plugins in <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-essential-kit-for-woocommerce-1/\" title=\"YITH Essential Kit for WooCommerce\"><strong>YITH Essential Kit for WooCommerce #1</strong></a>, a bundle of indispensable tools to make your WooCommerce site look more professional and be more user-friendly. Learn more about all WooCommerce plugins included and boost your WooCommerce site with a simple click!</p>\n<p>And if you want more, you can consider the premium version of YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking, with many more additional features.</p>\n<h4>Premium features of YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Send tracking data via email to customers as soon as the WooCommerce order is set as completed</li>\n<li>Tracking of the shipping available for a comprehensive and always updated list of carriers for your WooCommerce store</li>\n<li>Show a button in WooCommerce “My orders” page that takes customers automatically to carrier’s page and where they can find details of the shipping</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Suggestions</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking.</p>\n<h3>Translators</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress\" title=\"Translating WordPress\" rel=\"nofollow\">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/contact/\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking languages.</p>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:660:\"<p>Important: First of all, you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is essential for YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking to be work.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Download and unzip the downloaded file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking</code> from &#8220;Plugins&#8221; page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking will add a new tab called &#8220;Order tracking&#8221; in &#8220;YIT Plugins&#8221; menu item. There, you will find all Yithemes plugins with quick access to plugin setting page.</p>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:3778:\"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Important: First of all, you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is essential for YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking to be work.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Download and unzip the downloaded file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking</code> from &#8220;Plugins&#8221; page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking will add a new tab called &#8220;Order tracking&#8221; in &#8220;YIT Plugins&#8221; menu item. There, you will find all Yithemes plugins with quick access to plugin setting page.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>I always use the same carrier to ship my WooCommerce orders, may I set it as default carrier?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, sure, you can set the carrier name in the settings of YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking and for each new WooCommerce order you will find the field &#8220;carrier name&#8221; automatically filled with your default carrier.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Can I customise the message I want to send to customers?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can set your own text for your WooCommerce orders using the specific option available in YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking. You can also use some optional placeholders to specify carrier&#8217;s name, tracking code and shipping date.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>Is it compatible with all WordPress themes?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Compatibility with all themes is impossible, because they are too many, but generally if themes are developed according to WordPress and WooCommerce guidelines, YITH plugins are compatible with them.<br />\nYet, we can grant compatibility with themes developed by YIThemes, because they are constantly updated and tested with our plugins. Sometimes, especially when new versions are released, it might only require some time for them to be all updated, but you can be sure that they will be tested and will be working in a few days.</p>\n</p>\n<h4>How can I get support if my WooCommerce plugin is not working?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>If you have problems with our plugins or something is not working as it should, first follow this preliminary steps:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Test the plugin with a WordPress default theme, to be sure that the error is not caused by the theme you are currently using.</li>\n<li>Deactivate all plugins you are using and check if the problem is still occurring.</li>\n<li>Ensure that you plugin version, your theme version and your WordPress and WooCommerce version (if required) are updated and that the problem you are experiencing has not already been solved in a later plugin update.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If none of the previous listed actions helps you solve the problem, then, submit a ticket in the forum and describe your problem accurately, specify WordPress and WooCommerce versions you are using and any other information that might help us solve your problem as quickly as possible. Thanks!</p>\n</p>\n<h4>How can I get more features for my WooCommerce plugin?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can get more features with the premium version of YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking, available on <a href=\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/\" title=\"YITH order traking WooCommerce plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\">YIThemes page</a>. Here you can read more about the premium features of the plugin and make it give it its best shot!</p>\n</p>\n<h4>How can I try the full-featured plugin?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>If you want to see a demonstration version of the premium version of YITH WooCommerce Order Tracking, you can see that in <a href=\"http://plugins.yithemes.com/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/\" title=\"WooCommerce plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\">this page</a>. Browse it and try all options available so that you can see how your plugin looks like.</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:1840:\"<h4>Version 1.1.2 &#8211; Released: Apr 30, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: YITH Plugin Framework.</li>\n<li>Tweak: tested up to WordPress 4.7.4.</li>\n<li>Tweak: changed plugin tags.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.1 &#8211; Released: Mar 24, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New:  Support to WooCommerce 3.0.0-RC1</li>\n<li>Update: YITH Plugin Framework</li>\n<li>Fix: YITH Plugin Framework initialization.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.0 &#8211; Released: Jan 17, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: WordPress 4.7 ready</li>\n<li>Updated: WooCommerce 2.6 100% compatible</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.9 &#8211; Released: May 04, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: missing YITH Plugin FW files</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.8 &#8211; Released: May 02, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated: plugin compatible with WordPress 4.5</li>\n<li>Updated: plugin author name</li>\n<li>Updated: YITH Plugin Framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.7 &#8211; Released: Oct 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: update YITH Plugin framework.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.6 &#8211; Released: Oct 27, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: changed text domain from ywot to yith-woocommerce-order-tracking</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.5 &#8211; Released: Sep 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: error on changing order status when picked up checkbox is not checked.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.4 &#8211; Released: Aug 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: update YITH Plugin framework.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.3 &#8211; Released: Jun 25, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: WPML compatibility issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.2 &#8211; Released: Feb 17, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Dates are now shown in WordPress date format.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 &#8211; Released: Feb 16, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed: Default carrier sometimes was not correctly selected on new orders</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 &#8211; Released: Feb 13, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:2423:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1606380\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1606380\" alt=\"This is the setting page for the YITH wooCommerce Order Tracking. You can find it in &quot;YIT Plugins&quot; menu. You can configure a default carrier name and customize the message that will be shown in WooCommerce order details page.\"></a><p>This is the setting page for the YITH wooCommerce Order Tracking. You can find it in \"YIT Plugins\" menu. You can configure a default carrier name and customize the message that will be shown in WooCommerce order details page.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1606380\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1606380\" alt=\"From admin WooCommerce order page, you can see if the order has already been picked up by the carrier.\"></a><p>From admin WooCommerce order page, you can see if the order has already been picked up by the carrier.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1606380\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1606380\" alt=\"From admin WooCommerce order detail page, you can set details about carrier name, track number and date of shipping.\"></a><p>From admin WooCommerce order detail page, you can set details about carrier name, track number and date of shipping.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1606380\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1606380\" alt=\"In customer &quot;Orders&quot; page, a button will appear to show tracking of WooCommerce orders that have been shipped.\"></a><p>In customer \"Orders\" page, a button will appear to show tracking of WooCommerce orders that have been shipped.</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1606380\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1606380\" alt=\"In customer &quot;Orders&quot; page, you will find details about the shipment of your WooCommerce order.\"></a><p>In customer \"Orders\" page, you will find details about the shipment of your WooCommerce order.</p></li></ol>\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:117:\"Add an easy tool to manage order shipping information of your shop and to notified your customers about the shipping.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.1.2.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:5:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1606380\";s:7:\"caption\";s:225:\"This is the setting page for the YITH wooCommerce Order Tracking. You can find it in \"YIT Plugins\" menu. You can configure a default carrier name and customize the message that will be shown in WooCommerce order details page.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1606380\";s:7:\"caption\";s:102:\"From admin WooCommerce order page, you can see if the order has already been picked up by the carrier.\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1606380\";s:7:\"caption\";s:116:\"From admin WooCommerce order detail page, you can set details about carrier name, track number and date of shipping.\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1606380\";s:7:\"caption\";s:110:\"In customer \"Orders\" page, a button will appear to show tracking of WooCommerce orders that have been shipped.\";}i:5;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1606380\";s:7:\"caption\";s:94:\"In customer \"Orders\" page, you will find details about the shipment of your WooCommerce order.\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:7:\"carrier\";s:7:\"carrier\";s:8:\"delivery\";s:8:\"delivery\";s:8:\"shipping\";s:8:\"shipping\";s:8:\"tracking\";s:8:\"tracking\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";s:11:\"woocommerce\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:14:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.5\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.6\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.7\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.7.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.8\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.8.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.9\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.0.9.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:80:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.1.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"trunk\";s:74:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking.zip\";}s:11:\"donate_link\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"icons\";a:1:{s:2:\"1x\";s:84:\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-order-tracking/assets/icon-128x128.jpg?rev=1461215\";}s:12:\"contributors\";a:0:{}}}s:34:\"yith-woocommerce-badges-management\";a:6:{s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"YITH WooCommerce Badge Management\";s:4:\"slug\";s:34:\"yith-woocommerce-badges-management\";s:15:\"premium_constat\";s:17:\"YITH_WCBM_PREMIUM\";s:11:\"premium-dir\";s:33:\"yith-woocommerce-badge-management\";s:4:\"file\";s:8:\"init.php\";s:7:\"wp_info\";a:26:{s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"YITH WooCommerce Badge Management\";s:4:\"slug\";s:34:\"yith-woocommerce-badges-management\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.3.5\";s:6:\"author\";s:43:\"<a href=\"http://yithemes.com/\">YITHEMES</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:39:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes\";s:8:\"requires\";s:3:\"4.0\";s:6:\"tested\";s:5:\"4.8.1\";s:6:\"rating\";i:80;s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:15;i:4;i:1;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:1;i:1;i:4;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:21;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:5;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:0;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:6000;s:10:\"downloaded\";i:61972;s:12:\"last_updated\";s:22:\"2017-08-04 11:49am GMT\";s:5:\"added\";s:10:\"2015-03-25\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:71:\"https://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/\";s:8:\"sections\";a:5:{s:11:\"description\";s:1362:\"<p>Make your website more attractive with badges inviting customers to buy. It is not just a matter of appearance, it has been proved to increase sales up to 55%. Badges are an interesting tool, because they act on users&#8217; mind as spotlights that draw their attention upon a specific product, a specific offer, or attract them and make their interest higher and their will to purchase increases. Try YIThemes badges, highly customisable, in colour, text and position. Yet, a suggestion: do not exaggerate! A different badge for each product is like putting none upon them.</p>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>A specific panel to create unlimited textual badges. Options allow to set badge colour, text, text colour and badge position.</li>\n<li>5 image badges included in the plugin, with a graphic by YIThemes.</li>\n<li>A select menu for each product to choose the type of badge to set.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Gợi ý</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Badge Management, you can <a href=\"mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;\" title=\"Your Inspiration Themes\" rel=\"nofollow\">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Badge Management.</p>\n<h3>Phiên dịch</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>English (Default)</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:12:\"installation\";s:440:\"<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management</code> from Plugins page</li>\n</ol>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management will add a new submenu called &#8220;Badge Management&#8221; under &#8220;YIT Plugins&#8221; menu. Here you are able to configure all the plugin settings.</p>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:5430:\"<h4>1.3.5 &#8211; Released: Aug 04, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; use woocommerce_single_product_image_thumbnail_html</li>\n<li>Dev &#8211; added yith_wcbm_get_badge filter</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.4 &#8211; Released: May 09, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge saving</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; hidden badges in feeds</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; removed badges in wishlist table of YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.3 &#8211; Released: Apr 11, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 3.0.1</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; post thumbnail issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.2 &#8211; Released: Apr 05, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 3.0.0</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge saving</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.1 &#8211; Released: Mar 31, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 3.0.0-RC2</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; removed inline badge styles</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.3.0 &#8211; Released: Mar 10, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.7.0-RC1</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.7.3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.13 &#8211; Released: Jan 27, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge style issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.12 &#8211; Released: Dec 23, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; duplicate badges</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; removed badge permalink</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.11 &#8211; Released: Oct 26, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; added missing files</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; hidden badges in Storefront Sticky Add to Cart</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.10 &#8211; Released: Sep 23, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.6.1</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badges in YITH WooCommerce Recently Viewed Products emails hidden because causing graphical issues</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badges in YITH WooCommerce Questions and Answers emails hidden because causing graphical issues</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; issues in combination with Storefront Sticky Add to Cart</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge styles W3C</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.9 &#8211; Released: Jul 08, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.5.3</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.6.2</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to ajax loading of product thumbnails</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Italian language</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.8 &#8211; Released: Apr 29, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.5.1</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.5.5</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to Flatsome</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Frequently Bought Together</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Save for Later</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCoomerce Ajax Search</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Product Bundles</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; prevent badges from showing in WooCommerce emails</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.7 &#8211; Released: Jan 22, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.4.1</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.5</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; hidden badges in WooCommerce mini-cart</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; fixed minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.6 &#8211; Released: Dec 21, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; fixed minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.5 &#8211; Released: Dec 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.4</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.4.12</li>\n<li>New &#8211; possibility to show/hide badges in sidebars</li>\n<li>New &#8211; possibility to show/hide WooCommerce default &#8220;On Sale&#8221; badge when the product has another badge.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.3 &#8211; Released: Dec 01, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; fixed minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2 &#8211; Released: Nov 09, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Compatibility with more themes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.1 &#8211; Released: Oct 28, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.9 &#8211; Released: Aug 21, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WordPress 4.3</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; removed badges in cart and checkout</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.7 &#8211; Released: Aug 14, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce 2.4.4</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.6 &#8211; Released: Aug 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WordPress 4.2.4</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce 2.4.2</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; WPML deprecated functions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.5 &#8211; Released: Jul 24, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; WPML Compatibility</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Compatibility with more themes</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Bug with widget sidebar on header</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.4 &#8211; Released: Jul 10, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce shortcodes</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Compatibility with more themes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.3 &#8211; Released: Jul 03, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge display in widget top related product</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2 &#8211; Released: Jun 19, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Wrong admin css handle</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1 &#8211; Released: May 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommce 2.3.9</li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Default language file</li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Plugin framework</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Can&#8217;t make a badge issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0 &#8211; Released: May 08, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WordPress 4.2.2</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce 2.3.8</li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Default language file</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Duplicate product image in shop loop</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0 &#8211; Released: Mar 25, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:3:\"faq\";s:486:\"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management</code> from Plugins page</li>\n</ol>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management will add a new submenu called &#8220;Badge Management&#8221; under &#8220;YIT Plugins&#8221; menu. Here you are able to configure all the plugin settings.</p>\n</p>\n\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:2571:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1611885\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1611885\" alt=\"Admin: Badges list\"></a><p>Admin: Badges list</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1611885\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=1611885\" alt=\"Admin: Add new custom badge\"></a><p>Admin: Add new custom badge</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1611885\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=1611885\" alt=\"Admin: Add new image badge\"></a><p>Admin: Add new image badge</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1611885\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=1611885\" alt=\"Admin: Add badge to product\"></a><p>Admin: Add badge to product</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1611885\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-5.png?rev=1611885\" alt=\"Frontend: Shop page\"></a><p>Frontend: Shop page</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/screenshot-6.png?rev=1611885\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/yith-woocommerce-badges-management/assets/scre